===Verb===
{{en-verb|endures|enduring|endured}}

# {{transitive}} To [[continue]] or [[carry on]] with something, [[despite]] [[obstacle]]s or [[hardship]]s.
# {{transitive}} To [[tolerate]] or [[put up]] with something [[unpleasant]].
# {{intransitive}} To [[last]].
# {{intransitive}} To [[suffer]] [[patiently]].

